description: If I were to travel back in time and give some advice to my younger self, what would that be? Become friends with your impostor syndrome, because it's part of you and it's not going away ;) But if you learn to listen to it in a different way, it can be your strength - speaking up about what you don't know can actually help you make your team better, no matter how junior or new to the project you are.
title: What I wish someone told me 10 years ago - Be loud about what you don't know
